column5: now i know where all my sons tackle goes...
Time for a vest, or wading jacket or sling pack, lol.
Did that icefishing,  camera dropped from my shirt pocket no bounce, straight in.
Never done that but that must be an awful feeling!

OK, so the truth comes out.... There is no way he is my Son. Loosing tackle like that in the river and being caught on tape is just hilarious!!!  I like the first 2 videos you posted as well. And do you think there is a shortage of COs???  Cheers, Ron...
hmmm, let's see, YES!!! Of course we already know this.

wont go there ron .. its horrible this year.. every day netting and grabbing with hands. in the middle of the day.. its just nasty.. by the way your son picked up 2 more bags of garbage .. and 8 fish bodies  i did not get  video of natives going to spear fish .. and saying they would be back in the spring  to get rainbows the  i have edited to show the boy and the girl that are coming to do it ..  Ron it will just up your child support.
